Package: ka9q-radio
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 ka9q-radio-common,
 libcap2-bin, systemd, udev
Description: KA9Q multichannel SDR server
 Multichannel software-defined radio "spectrum server"
 with multicast control and data
 
Package: ka9q-radio-common
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 systemd
Description: common files for ka9q-radio
 Common files for ka9q-radio and ka9q-radio's user commands and daemons

Package: ka9q-radio-hfdl
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 systemd
Description: HFDL subsystem for ka9q-radio
 HFDL (High Frequency Data Link) is a packet radio system used by commercial
 airliners over oceans and remote areas. This package decodes all known
 HFDL data channels. It requires manual installation of the dumphfdl and
 libacars packages (not supplied as standard Debian packages)

Package: ka9q-radio-packet
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 systemd
Description: AX.25/aprs subsystem for ka9q-radio
 Provides AFSK AX.25 decoder, APRS extractor and feeder
 
Package: ka9q-radio-recordings
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 systemd
Description: recording subsystem for ka9q-radio
 Provides some sample configurations for automatic recording of groups of audio
 channels from ka9q-radio's radiod

Package: ka9q-radio-horus
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 systemd
Description: demodulation subsystem for horus balloon telemetry
 Decode balloon telemetry in the Horus (VK5QI) format
 requires horus_demod package to be manually installed

Package: ka9q-radio-ft
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 systemd
Description: FT4/FT8/WSPR skimmers for ka9q-radio
 records and decodes FT4, FT8 and WSPR transmissions, logs in /var/log/ft[48].log, wspr.log
 
Package: ka9q-radio-control
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 ka9q-radio-common
Description: Control program for ka9q-radio
 Interactive channel control program for ka9q-radio; uses ncurses
 
Package: ka9q-radio-monitor
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 ka9q-radio-common
Description: Multicast stream audio monitor for ka9q-radio
 Interactive multicast RTP stream monitor for ka9q-radio, uses ncurses,
 handles multiple channels, supports pcm, opus, u-law, a-law
 
Package: ka9q-radio-tools
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line tools for ka9q-radio
 Shell command line tools for interacting with ka9q-radio over the net
 
Package: ka9q-radio-airspy
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ka9q-radio (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Airspy device plugin for ka9q-radio
 ka9q-radio plugin for the Airspy R2, Airspy Mini SDR front ends
	     
