 ka9q-radio-funcube,
 ka9q-radio-hackrf,
 ka9q-radio-hydrasdr,
 ka9q-radio-rtlsdr,
 ka9q-radio-rx888
Description: meta package for all components of ka9q-radio
 Brings in the radio daemon radiod, the command line tools, control monitor and the device plugins





